title: Zoo Zoom Famous: Life Hacks From A Professional Cricket (10/10/22)
description:
Mindy wants to take the internet by storm with her ZooZoom animal life hack videos. For this video demonstration, Mindy is showing off how crickets use tools to find their one true love! When Guy Raz steps up to help her film, will they be able to create the next big viral video?! Originally aired 5/3/21.
